title: Mister Miracle v1 19-25 Steve Englehart - Steve Gerber
description:
A bit of Gerber-Englehart exotica. Their few issues of Mister Miracle before the series was canceled.  

Thanks to the scanners and seeders. I pulled these from a very thorough Jack Kirby New Gods/Fourth World torrent that you can find pretty easily doing a search for those terms or \"Kirby Pack.\" It might be worth checking out if you haven\&#039;t already and if you\&#039;re following the current Death of the New Gods saga.
